engChrName: *sigh* I can't help but worry about her sometimes. She's a little too singleminded for her own good.
engSearchText:
*sigh* I can't help but worry about her sometimes.
She's a little too singleminded for her own good.
jpnChrName: ふう、大丈夫かな先輩…… 何にでも一途すぎる性分だし。
jpnSearchText:
ふう、大丈夫かな先輩……
何にでも一途すぎる性分だし。

engChrName: Though I suppose that's why she's the genuine article...unlike me.
engSearchText:
Though I suppose that's why she's the genuine
article...unlike me.
jpnChrName: ……だからこそ私と違って “本物”なんでしょうけど。
jpnSearchText:
……だからこそ私と違って
“本物”なんでしょうけど。
……ああ、お疲れ様です。

engChrName: I see... So that's where the 'filming' will be taking place. Just as we thought.
engSearchText:
I see... So that's where the 'filming' will be
taking place. Just as we thought.
jpnChrName: なるほど…… “ロケ地”は想定通りでしたか。
jpnSearchText:
なるほど……
“ロケ地”は想定通りでしたか。

engChrName: The only question now is who the final cast will be. We don't have long until the shoot begins, it seems.
engSearchText:
The only question now is who the final cast will be.
We don't have long until the shoot begins, it seems.
jpnChrName: すると最終的な配役は── クランクインも間もなくみたいですね。
jpnSearchText:
すると最終的な配役は──
クランクインも間もなくみたいですね。
